Interface CsvTable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<CsvRow>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CsvTableImpl
    public interface CsvTable
extends java.lang.Iterable<CsvRow>
    A single table loaded from ER/Studio's .DM1 file. A CsvTable can be iterated over its rows containing data that are of type CsvRow
